snippet.title: Hidden In My Paradise - Official Trailer | Latin American Games Showcase
snippet.description: See gameplay and check out the colorful, cozy world of Hidden In My Paradise in this trailer for the upcoming hidden-object game where you can create little paradises. Get ready to hide objects, decorate, and complete missions when Hidden In My Paradise launches on PC.
